\cf2 Save the following identified pages and features of the Xponent mini app:\
\
### Pages\
1. **Dashboard Page**  \
   - Central hub summarizing user metrics, ecosystem highlights, token balances, and actionable recommendations.  \
   - Includes shortcuts to key features and links to partner platforms.\
\
2. **Token & Rewards Page**  \
   - Displays token balances (SuperrCoins, XO tokens, and influencer tokens), recent transactions, and opportunities to earn more.  \
   - Allows users to redeem or convert tokens and track milestone rewards.\
\
3. **Profile & Settings Page**  \
   - Centralized control for user identity, linked platform accounts, notification preferences, and data sharing.  \
   - Includes options to manage security, view/export data, and access support.\
\
4. **Workflows & Automations Page**  \
   - Allows users to create and manage rules connecting triggers and actions across the ecosystem.  \
   - Includes a list of existing workflows, editing functionality, and logs for tracking workflow executions.\
\
5. **Search & Discovery Page**  \
   - Aggregates search functionality across all partner platforms.  \
   - Enables users to find courses (AIDT), projects (Open Verse), influencer campaigns (Virion Labs), and talent opportunities (NexHire).  \
   - Includes filtering options and direct links to partner platforms.\
\
6. **Onboarding/Tutorial Page**  \
   - Step-by-step walkthrough for new users to understand the Xponent ecosystem.  \
   - Covers Dashboard, Tokens, Workflows, Search, and AI assistant functionalities.  \
   - Includes a progress tracker, ability to skip or revisit, and a final summary.\
\
### Features\
1. **Unified User Profile & Identity**  \
   - Linked accounts for AIDT, Open Verse, Virion Labs, and NexHire.  \
   - User-centric settings for privacy, notifications, and data sharing.\
\
2. **Cross-Platform Token Management**  \
   - Token balances for all integrated platforms.  \
   - Redemption and conversion tools.  \
   - Earning opportunities and milestone tracking.\
\
3. **AI-Driven Guidance**  \
   - AI assistant in Telegram to help navigate the app, answer questions, and provide contextual suggestions.  \
   - Integration with mini app pages for seamless handoff between chat and app.\
\
4. **Workflows & Automations**  \
   - Trigger-action workflows to automate cross-platform activities.  \
   - Easy-to-use builder with clear triggers (e.g., completing a course) and actions (e.g., earning tokens, notifications).\
\
5. **Cross-Platform Search**  \
   - Unified search engine with filtering options for courses, projects, campaigns, and jobs.  \
   - Links users directly to partner platforms for detailed interactions.\
\
6. **Notifications & Updates (Optional Future Feature)**  \
   - Aggregated updates from across the ecosystem.  \
   - Persistent record of achievements, announcements, and ecosystem milestones.\
\
7. **Help & Support (Optional Future Feature)**  \
   - Repository of FAQs and self-service support.  \
   - Direct access to customer support if integrated.\
\
This structure ensures the mini app serves as a central hub for users, tying together all aspects of the Xponent ecosystem seamlessly.\cell 
